## S 8. Open Compose Dialog (for original posts)

🚨 **Verified 2026-03-28:** Compose dialog is identical to reply/quote dialog — same `[role="dialog"]`, `[role="textbox"]`, "Post" button. Use S 5 from BROWSER-core.md to type + submit.

**ONE evaluate — click Create button in nav:**

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 1000)); var createSvg = document.querySelector('svg[aria-label=\"Create\"]'); if (!createSvg) return { error: 'no Create button' }; var btn = createSvg.closest('div[role=\"button\"]'); if (!btn) return { error: 'no parent button' }; btn.click(); await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000)); var dialog = document.querySelector('[role=\"dialog\"]'); var textbox = dialog ? dialog.querySelector('[role=\"textbox\"][contenteditable=\"true\"]') : null; return { dialogReady: !!textbox }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

If `dialogReady: true` → proceed to BROWSER-core.md S 5 (type + submit).
If `dialogReady: false` → retry once. Still fails → skip, log error.
